- **Languages supported:** {{Languages}}

## 1) Goals
1. Inspire trust fast (showcase results, credentials, hygiene).
2. Drive appointments (sticky CTA, WhatsApp, click-to-call).
3. Rank for local SEO (“dental implants in {{Locality}}”, etc.).
4. Educate with crisp visuals and plain-English explanations.

## 2) Tech & Quality Bar
- **Stack:** Next.js (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui + Framer Motion.
- **Design:** Clean, modern, white/soft pastel palette; generous whitespace; rounded 2xl; subtle depth.
- **Perf:** Lighthouse ≥ 95 (Perf/SEO/Best Practices/Accessibility). LCP < 2.5s on 4G, CLS < 0.1.
- **A11y:** WCAG 2.2 AA (focus states, ARIA landmarks, form labels, color contrast, skip link).
- **SEO:** Static metadata per route; OpenGraph/Twitter cards; XML sitemap; robots.txt.

## 3) Site Map (routes & intent)
- **/** (Home): hero, trust stack, services overview, doctor creds, testimonials, badges, awards, clinic tour, CTA.
- **/implants** (Primary money page).
- **/rct-endo**
- **/aligners-orthodontics**
- **/cosmetic-smile-makeover**
- **/general-dentistry**
- **/doctors** (team bios with credentials & memberships).
- **/pricing** (transparent ranges + EMI).
- **/before-after** (gallery with consent).
- **/reviews** (Google review embed + filters).
- **/contact** (map, parking/landmarks, form, WhatsApp).
- **/book** (booking flow).
- **/blogs** (educational posts).
- **/locations/{{locality}}** (create templated local landing pages for 10–20 neighborhoods).
- **/privacy** and **/terms**.

## 4) Global UI
- **Header:** Logo, sticky nav, CTA buttons: “Book Appointment”, “WhatsApp”, “Call”.
- **Footer:** Address, hours, map, quick links, accreditation logos, social, emergency note.
- **Sticky Contact Dock (mobile):** Call | WhatsApp | Book.
- **Trust Stack (persistent across site):** badges (NABH/ISO/IDA/ICOI), review count (target 4.8★ 500+), sterilization SOP, awards logos, media mentions.
- **Micro-copy:** Pain-reduction, warranties, genuine empathy.

## 5) Home Page Content (generate polished copy + UI)
- **Hero:** Headline (“Implants & Advanced Dentistry in {{City}}”), subheadline (pain-free, CBCT-planned), 2 CTAs (Book, WhatsApp), trust badges row, above-the-fold clinic image.
- **Services Grid (5 cards):** Implants / RCT / Aligners / Cosmetic / General — each with icon, 2-line value prop, “Know more”.
- **Why {{ClinicName}}:** bullet list (experience, tech: CBCT/Waterlase/IOS, sterilization, EMI).
- **Before-After Carousel:** 6–10 cases with captions (case type, timeframe).
- **Doctor Spotlight:** photo, credentials, memberships (IDA, ICOI, AAID), conferences, publications.
- **Social Proof:** Review highlight cards + link to /reviews.
- **Clinic Tour:** 6 photos (reception, op room, sterilization area, CBCT, aligner corner, recovery).
- **FAQ (accordion):** 8–10 common questions (pain, cost, warranty, downtime, diet).
- **Final CTA:** “Free Virtual Pre-Consult Today”.

## 6) Service Pages (structure & content)
**For each page:** /implants, /rct-endo, /aligners-orthodontics, /cosmetic-smile-makeover, /general-dentistry

- **Hero:** procedure name + immediate benefit (e.g., “Eat Confidently Again”).
- **Explainer:** 3–5 step process with icons (Assessment → Planning → Treatment → Review → Maintenance).
- **Outcomes:** bullets with patient-friendly metrics (success rate ranges, healing times).
- **Pricing & EMI:** transparent ranges with inclusions; EMI calculator snippet.
- **Candidacy Checklist:** who’s a good candidate; contraindications (plain language).
- **Tech We Use:** CBCT, intra-oral scanner, guided surgery; brand-agnostic.
- **Before–After block:** 3–6 relevant cases.
- **FAQ (schema-ready):** 6–8 Qs.
- **CTA strip:** “Book Implant Assessment” (+WhatsApp).

## 7) Reviews & Gallery
- **/reviews:** Filter by treatment; average rating; highlight 5 most recent; “Write a review” link.
- **/before-after:** Masonry grid; each case card has (problem → treatment → result duration) tags.

## 8) Booking & Forms
- **/book:** multi-step form (name, phone, treatment interest, preferred time, consent). Validate; show confirmation + ICS calendar download; send to {{Email}} + WhatsApp.
- **WhatsApp Deep Link:** prefilled message “Hi {{ClinicName}}, I’d like to book an {{Service}} on {{Date}}.”
- **Call tracking:** tel: links with event tracking.

## 9) Local SEO Pack
- Create **/locations/{{locality}}** pages (auto-generate 10–20): intro paragraph, nearby landmarks, schema `LocalBusiness`, embedded map, NAP data, localized reviews, CTAs, internal links to services.
- On-page: H1 with locality, meta title `Dental Implants in {{Locality}} | {{ClinicName}}`, FAQ targeting “cost, pain, time, EMI”.

## 10) Copy Tone & Brand
- Friendly, expert, reassuring. Avoid jargon. Plain English. Short paragraphs, scannable lists.
- Use INR currency. Mention EMI & warranties clearly. Emphasize hygiene and pain management.

## 11) Components to Implement
- `SectionHero`, `ServiceCard`, `StatsBar`, `BeforeAfterCarousel`, `DoctorCard`, `ReviewList`, `FAQAccordion`, `ContactDock`, `EMICalculator`, `LocationCard`, `BookingForm`.
- Animations: subtle fade/slide on scroll, 200–300ms; reduced-motion support.

## 12) Structured Data (schema.org)
- `LocalBusiness` / `Dentist` (name, logo, sameAs, phone, geo, openingHours).
- `Product` for each service (name, description, priceRange).
- `FAQPage` on FAQs.
- `Review` / `AggregateRating` where applicable.
- JSON-LD in `<script type="application/ld+json">…</script>`.

## 13) Analytics & Events
- Add GA4 + basic event tags: `click_call`, `click_whatsapp`, `submit_booking`, `cta_hero`, `view_before_after`.
- Cookie notice (minimal, non-intrusive).

## 14) Performance & Images
- Use next/image with responsive sizes; lazy load below the fold; prefetch hero.
- SVG icons; compress all assets. Preconnect to fonts; system font stack preferred or 1 web font (display: swap).

## 15) Security & Privacy
- HTTPS, CSRF on forms, server-side email sending. Simple privacy policy page.
- Consent checkbox for contacting via WhatsApp/SMS.

